{
  "texts": [
    "Liu et al. [162] investigated the power allocation of OFDM-based ISAC system for performance enhancement.",
    "To ensure both satisfactory communication and sensing performance, a number of parameters of the OFDM waveform were jointly optimized by Liu et al. [163].",
    "They also investigated the performance trade-off between the two functionalities in [164].",
    "Specifically, the weighted sum of the CRB of parameter estimation and achievable rate was minimized by optimizing the weighting coefficient of each subcarrier.",
    "Liyanaarachchi et al. [165] filled the empty subcarriers of the OFDM waveform with optimized frequency domain samples to improve the detection capability."
  ]
}